extendedInfo.description: This is the free version of the Exynos Pregnancy Calculator app that can be use to calculate the Gestational age and Expected delivery date for mothers. It has all the information the will guide mothers about the development of their babies each week. This is also a helpful tool for midwifes to replace the Maternity wheel.*** Disclaimer This app is for information purposes only and are not a substitute for professional medical or health advice, examination, diagnosis, or treatment. Information provided here is not intended as specific medical advice. In the event of an emergency, please call 911.Always seek the advice of your physician or other qualified health professional. Do not delay seeking or disregard medical advice based on information on this app. Medical information changes rapidly and some information may be out of date. The information should not be used to diagnose, treat, cure, or prevent any disease without the supervision of a medical doctor. Thank you.
